  "title": "Senior Beauty Consultant (Retail)",
  "description": "<p>Affinity Cosmetics is hiring for Beauty Sales Consultant (Retail) for our multiple locations around Singapore.</p>\n<p>Join the Affinity team today and become part of the dream.</p>\n<p>Job Benefits</p>\n<p>- Training by international professionals</p>\n<p>- Opportunities are available for all those with a passion for beauty and determination for success.</p>\n<p>- Learning and growing daily with the team</p>\n<p>- Island wide work locations with easy access to MRT stations</p>\n<p>- Bonus and motivating incentives</p>\n<p>Job Requirement</p>\n<p>- Roaster planning</p>\n<p>- Staff arrangment / Staff matters</p>\n<p>- Meeting at office once a week</p>\n<p>- Able to stand long working hours</p>\n<p>- Commit to retail hours</p>\n<p>- Able to work on Weekends and Public Holidays</p>\n<p>- Aggressive Selling</p>\n<p>- Approaching customer at doorstep</p>\n<p>- Drive and achieve individual sales target on monthly basis, in a team environment</p>\n<p>- Demonstrate and promote our product</p>\n<p>- Good knowledge in skincare</p>\n<p>- Relevant Beauty Retail experience</p>\n<p>- Build and establish new customer prospects</p>\n<p>- Strong customer service mentality</p>\n<p>- Good team player with a positive personality</p>\n<p>- Creating and nurturing a strong relationship with clients</p>\n<p>- Good team player with a positive personality</p>\n<p>- Deadsea sales personnel plus point / Non experienced candidates are welcome *training provided</p>\n<p>- Manage daily operating activities in the store</p>\n<p>- Daily inventory stock tally</p>\n<p>Interested Candidates can apply as below:</p>\n<p>Email: hr2@affinity-cosmetics.com.sg</p>\n<p>Whatsspp: +65 9788 0466</p>",
